todolist.ui

Class TaskWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • todolist.ui.TaskWrapper

  • public class TaskWrapper
extends Object
    TaskWrapper is the wrapper class for Task class. It wraps each attribute into a property for display.
    Author:
    Huang Lie Jun (A0123994W)
